<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>维护中 ｜ {{ site_name }}</title>
  <meta name="description" content="站点维护中，请稍后再试。">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="{{ site.theme_color }}">
  {% include "partials/theme_init.html.j2" %}
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex">
  {% if site_url %}
  <link rel="canonical" href="{{ site_url }}/maintenance.html">
  {% endif %}
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles/gallery.css?v={{ static_version }}">
</head>
<body class="page-error with-sidebar">
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main-content">跳到主要内容</a>
  {% include "partials/topbar.html.j2" %}
  <main id="main-content" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="home-layout">
      {% include "partials/sidebar_default.html.j2" %}
      <div class="home-main">
        <div class="error-main">
          <section class="error-hero">
            <div class="error-card">
              <div class="error-eyebrow">很抱歉</div>
              <h1 class="error-title">站点维护中</h1>
              <p class="error-lead">您浏览的页面正在维护或发布，请稍后再来。已发布内容仍可正常访问。</p>
              <div class="error-actions">
                <a class="btn primary" href="/">回到首页</a>
                <a class="btn ghost" href="/status/">查看状态</a>
              </div>
              <div class="error-meta">
                <span class="error-code">503</span>
                <span class="error-tag">Maintenance</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <figure class="error-figure">
              <div class="error-figure-frame">
                <img src="/static/images/error-figure.webp" alt="维护中的小人插画" width="950" height="1200" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
              </div>
              <figcaption>维护期间如需帮助，可先查看状态页了解进度。</figcaption>
            </figure>
          </section>
          <section class="error-tips" aria-label="提示">
            <div class="error-tip">
              <h2>提示</h2>
              <ul>
                <li>维护完成后页面会自动恢复访问。</li>
                <li>若你是管理员，可检查发布或维护日志。</li>
                <li>长时间未恢复时，请稍后刷新或查看状态。</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="error-tip">
              <h2>为什么会维护？</h2>
              <p>维护通常用于发布新内容、清理缓存或进行系统优化。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="error-tip">
              <h2>感谢理解</h2>
              <p>感谢你的耐心等待，我们会尽快恢复服务。</p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <script src="/static/js/ui.js?v={{ static_version }}" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
